					</div>
					<p class="text-darkgray">
						Banging, rattling, whistling, or grinding sounds from your heat pump are not normal and typically indicate a
						mechanical issue that requires professional attention.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Insufficient Heat or Cooling -->
				<div class="bg-lightgray p-6 rounded-lg">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none"
