						</svg>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary">Rising Energy Bills</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-darkgray">
						An unexpected increase in your energy bills without a corresponding increase in usage often indicates that
						your heat pump is operating inefficiently and needs service.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Frequent Cycling -->
				<div class="bg-lightgray p-6 rounded-lg">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none"
