						</svg>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary">Ice Buildup</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-darkgray">
						While some frost is normal during winter operation, excessive ice buildup on your outdoor unit indicates a
						problem with the defrost cycle or refrigerant levels that needs immediate attention.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Age of System -->
				<div class="bg-lightgray p-6 rounded-lg">
