						</svg>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary">Age of System</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-darkgray">
						If your heat pump is more than 10-15 years old, it may require more frequent service to maintain efficiency
						and reliability. Regular maintenance becomes even more important as systems age.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
